text: John Duus (born 11 April 1955) is a Norwegian sport shooter. He competed in 50 metre rifle, prone and 50 metre rifle three positions at the 1984 Summer Olympics in Los Angeles. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Norway Category:Shooters at the 1984 Summer Olympics
